微信视频号、微信推广、抖音、快手、西瓜视频、知乎、百度搜索、手机APP（因为1级方向不清晰，2级机会抓的有些盲目，还需要逐步优化）<br>3级增长：公众号、视频号目前遇到了增长瓶，微信推广、知乎、百度搜索、手机APP增长放缓，抖音、快手、西瓜视频是新开辟的推广渠道，正在摸索中（整体增长放缓，需要反思原因）<br>4级成果：在之前的推广过程中，成功为公司带来了增长，但增长目前已经放缓，突破瓶颈还需要仔细研究。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":272948,"user_name":"TeddyPM","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1325117,"ip_address":"","ucode":"B066C2A8590DB3","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/38/3d/d6f1e2e6.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1610361486,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1610361486","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"斗罗大陆的7怪是一个很牛的增长团队","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":157331,"user_name":"上善若水","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1653332,"ip_address":"","ucode":"E3F15FB8576626","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/19/3a/54/72402617.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1575111414,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1575111414","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"机器学习吧","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":127214,"user_name":"见见","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1635257,"ip_address":"","ucode":"4FA6A15C874574","user_header":"http://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/0lUB4ZpQIh4thsgWR0QVeRrdKzbHhtT90vHticsByNO0ibWNSXtsvr3Fg8239AWA70WtrRDFYmQJtuCnO0kSz35g/132","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1566612212,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1566612212","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"产品负责。功能的取舍和流程的简化，操作的简化，怎么样明晰的减法让功能不缺失，但又傻瓜式操作是很头疼的事情。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":102291,"user_name":"水水","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1503115,"ip_address":"","ucode":"E33588CD8A627B","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/ef/8b/fa1ed4f7.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1560177607,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"36939","content":"加油。","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"Geek_Test","uid":"1568170","ctime":1560220655,"ip_address":"","comment_id":102291,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"1560177607","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"目前工作涉及的是3级增长，也就是执行方案那一层。但工作流程还是旧模式的发现问题或需求，然后做方案上线。<br>在尝试执行增长思维的时候，发现项目高阶用户洞察做的不够细致，无法找出产品跟竞品区别，也就是对于用户来说差异化定位区分不足，唯一的竞争壁垒是运营渠道的广泛。<br>现在自己面临的问题是如何去探寻用户差异化或是说寻找出用户特征的需求点。主要还是自己勇气不足，需要努力去找不同角色协作探寻这一点才好","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1568170,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/17/ed/aa/c2b9e399.jpg","nickname":"Geek_Test","note":"","ucode":"2A70B596E8F49D","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":453340,"discussion_content":"加油。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1560220655,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":1}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":92759,"user_name":"Mr.Wu","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1507464,"ip_address":"","ucode":"5680DAA9389024","user_header":"http://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/Q0j4TwGTfTKmMUtoRFVPYOnkvlFCesmM6iaDdElMicGv0faqYo2jmiay1fQySoxJyodsJUFM0cEdXK552gpu2hXWw/132","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1557322241,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1557322241","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"你好，我之前是从事数据分析工作的！在数据分析工作中遇到的问题就是提供很多优化建议，但到业务这边出于各种因素考虑，很难落地执行！<br>最近遇到一些机会，部门内业务市场业务主管升职，自己也通过争取，拿到了市场运营主管的岗位，于是就开始从流量，网络推广开始参与增长，目前还兼负产品的数据分析工作，无论从业务，还是产品，已经开始将增长思维带团队，目前遇到问题：<br>1.市场业务技能并不擅长，所以在做流量增长会遇到尝试很多实验，增长效果并不明显<br>2.团队成员对数据的认识还并不是很深入<br>3.整体目标就是营收增长（产品是付费工具），前期投入的时候总想着能不能保本，能不能有利润，这样目标让团队成员很困惑","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":89366,"user_name":"和小胖","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1180727,"ip_address":"","ucode":"406BD7AB987EBF","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/04/37/aa04f997.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1556159134,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1556159134","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"很多普通员工可能就接触不到文中的北极星指标，因为这个是大老板定的战略，普通的员工一般接触到的东西就到了比较细节的部分，所以一般直接接触到的是第3级增长。<br><br>所以普通员工可能对于之前几级根本没有话语权，但是依然有可为，做好自己这一级该做的事情，给自己数据提供好方案或者数据，给他们决策所需的。<br><br>虽然公司的产品自己没有话语权，但是自己的产品总归是有的，很多在公司内实现不了的想法，在自己的产品上可以去实践。<br><br>因此，增长不仅仅是公司的产品。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":88758,"user_name":"Di.","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1507387,"ip_address":"","ucode":"EDE4E5E82BA15A","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/17/00/3b/d613a604.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555994172,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555994172","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"北极星指标是制定方向，OKR是分解执行的过程","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":88527,"user_name":"求知鸟","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1309134,"ip_address":"","ucode":"76249BB4897629","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/f9/ce/4985c6fc.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555936027,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555936027","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"BI在我公司<br>参与发现增长机会：和增长经理讨论何时唤醒沉默用户（裂变活动来的用户唤醒，寒假用户唤醒），考虑是否缩短购买流程，是否下架某功能按钮等<br>打造闭关落地实施增长：参与需求评审，埋点设计，埋点开发，上线测试<br>总结增长规律：开屏触达用户最多，弹窗点击率最好，消息通知最舒适等。<br>以上<br>","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":87636,"user_name":"Farrishta","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1506034,"ip_address":"","ucode":"41B514AC5EBF50","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/fa/f2/390fa5e5.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555645613,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"31559","content":"很棒👍","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"jean0810","uid":"1392448","ctime":1555680933,"ip_address":"","comment_id":87636,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"scor