FBEFC","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/3d/48/4ed86ee5.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555564103,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555564103","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"学习了增长的4个方向，把4个增长级别结合到我公司的研发流程中，就产生了如下的的对应关系<br>1 级方向对应公司的【制定项目专题】，例如为标板增加代销业务、增加零售业务 <br>2 级方向对应【确定专题相关的场景和功能】，比如零售业务会涉及 商品模块，订单模块。那么订单模块的场景是什么功能改动点又是什么<br>3 级方向对应【功能的设计，开发，上线】<br>4 级方向是项目后总结,功能上线后市场需求反馈如何，用户是否满意，满意的原因是什么，不满意的原因是什么<br>我之前的工作主要涵盖了2,3,4级增长既根据公司明确的项目专题进行【确定功能范围和场景】，【功能的设计和上线跟踪】，【上线后的反馈跟踪】，参与1级增长方向的机会很少。<br><br>未来参与1级增长方向的方法主要有<br>1）从用户调研中思考是否能找到1级增长的业务点，并反馈给公司<br>2）调研其他相关2b产品思考是否能找到1级增长的业务点，反馈给公司","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":86963,"user_name":"白竹","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1020178,"ip_address":"","ucode":"249DD99ACBAAD9","user_header":"","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555487834,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555487834","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"凡事都有几个核心指标，然后围绕核心指标，做些工具落地。<br><br>指标细化分级是更明确，更能判断出优劣。<br><br>这就更考验领导或团队制定核心即1级增长目标的制定，对自己产品的，用户的定位有清楚认识。<br>","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":86721,"user_name":"Aggi","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1149405,"ip_address":"","ucode":"71F21996F46FD8","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/89/dd/802dacd4.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555433004,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555433004","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"职位:数据分析<br>北极星指标:用户增长<br>一级方向:粉丝增长<br>二级机会:粉丝运营<br>因为目前二级都还没做好，三级、四级就暂时还没有，不知道这么理解对不？","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":86527,"user_name":"Lindm","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1415532,"ip_address":"","ucode":"31292436A81543","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/15/99/6c/f5f4414b.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555391504,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555391504","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"我能遇见到的是未来三年内，部门的增长模式是打造一款“通用”产品，不断的迭代更新，提高经济效益。通过这几讲，我理解到的增长是，能够促进社会，促进企业，促进个人持久化发展。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":86353,"user_name":"Tays","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1194344,"ip_address":"","ucode":"1211AEF35C958E","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/39/68/5f4894b6.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555372888,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555372888","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"当前是产品经理，目前主要涉及2、3， 其中部分参与1的内容. 作为一个偏向传统企业转型之作，目前的产品其实存在比较大的问题，没有明确目标，扩大现有优势，在推广上基本放弃线上推广，采用的依然是传统的电销、线下推广的模式. 我依然确信线上的推广是一个非常重要的渠道，所以通过自己的方式去完成部分2、3的内容，但是在没有其他方面支持的情况下，感觉收益甚微.<br><br>在项目中遇到一些业务方提的很多不合理需求，从他们角度觉得是为了增长，但是从开发角度、产品角度，觉得是一个很不合理的需求，我们希望从其他方面解决，而不是对产品大刀阔斧不合理修改（短期性，后期还需要还原）. 但是业务方负责人是整个项目总负责人，需求评审也未正常进行，我们只是负责他们提出的需求，没有反驳的机会","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":86345,"user_name":"faye","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1489207,"ip_address":"","ucode":"B4A7D1AFC4F1DC","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/b9/37/2868c5dd.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555370381,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"31028","content":"那是很久以前的了，现在都是突出额度","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"jean0810","uid":"1392448","ctime":1555382200,"ip_address":"","comment_id":86345,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555370381","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"我看到的宜人贷突出的特点是放款快，门槛低，利息低","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1392448,"avatar":"http://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/Q0j4TwGTfTKH4ILYLTcZjqWBjLb3D31mianUCcGExWfgFEiasV5xHuSZ9U4SuPqqsZoO8EJBVJ3km54ncHJibtRtA/132","nickname":"jean0810","note":"","ucode":"19B0B4E776F653","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":446981,"discussion_content":"那是很久以前的了，现在都是突出额度","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1555382200,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":86310,"user_name":"Haru","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1502999,"ip_address":"","ucode":"FBDA20F0F21885","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/ef/17/f827777d.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555344228,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555344228","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"视觉设计师，参与了3级落地。做需求的时候也会考虑产品层面的东西，也明白为什么那么干。可是需求完成了很少去分析数据，都是产品经理会分析。就算接触到数据了，也不是很懂怎么分析？<br>另外，想问，初创产品，有北极星指标，怎么找到1级定位的？怎么找到跟竞品的差异点？","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":86302,"user_name":"say something","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1499238,"ip_address":"","ucode":"89BE644CD8078E","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/e0/66/b6f28519.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555341723,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555341723","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"目前是产品运营，0.3个负责人<br>覆盖的范围：2级，3级<br>问题：卡在第3级中，目前主要测试哪个着陆页的转化效果是最好，当确定后会采用最优着陆页，后期大方向主要铺更多渠道资源，对于文案来说是个可以考虑的重要点，但是有两个问题：<br>1.公司重视粗暴形式去拉新，以量堆量，有点儿烧钱，不重优化，想快速获取新用户<br>2.对于痛点不够明确，没有深入了解用户对于我们app的痛点，策划推广位文案就更难（解决方案想法：利用活动形式的调查问卷，列出app的功能点，去各大推广位渠道进行收集，分析不同渠道的主要痛点，再使用不同的文案，吸引更多用户点击推广位进入着陆页，望老师指点～）","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":86285,"user_name":"ywqqjw","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1196128,"ip_address":"","ucode":"93058B43AE59DE","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/40/60/9164e54a.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555338311,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555338311","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"开发人员，目前处在第三级增长和四级成果上。在设计整个流程的时候还是会希望对于用户来说越简单越好，也尽量少的让用户在使用过程中做选择。对于用户使用较多的功能会有具体的数据来检测再进行复盘统计并对数据进行分析。","like_count":0}]}